   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Turn the ignition key to the ON position and then to START position, without waiting for the preheat light to go OFF. At the same time fully depress the accelerator.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Release the ignition key when the engine starts and release the accelerator pedal to a low idle position. Release the ignition key after engine starting and check the engine conditions.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
